Description: # PyPani
        A Python package for the Irrigation scheduler, PANI.
        
        ---------------
        
        ![PyPani Diagram](images/logo.png)
        
        --------------
        
        ## Example Run:
        To run manually:
        ``` python model.py 03/10/2018 322/2017```
        
        To build and test the package.
        
        ```pip3 install -e . ```
        
        Example data can be found in "tests" folder
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
